      "span_text": "Nevertheless, we should mention here that several of the theoretical arguments in Section 5 were inspired by Gröbner basis computations in the computational algebra system Magma [CITATION_4] and it would have been significantly more difficult, maybe even impossible, to obtain the classification in Theorem 1.1 without performing such computations."
